headline: Ryder System, Inc. Elects Tammy Romo to Its Board of Directors
summary: MIAMI, December 19, 2025--The board of directors of Ryder System, Inc. (NYSE: R) today announces the appointment of Tammy Romo, 63, to its board, effective January 5, 2026. Romo will serve as a member of the Audit and Finance Committees.
